data.description: Experience the charm of this predominantly single-story home located in The Heights at Stone Oak. Special touches abound, from the wood floors, cozy family room fireplace to an oversized game room upstairs complete with half bath. The updated kitchen is delightful, equipped with stainless steel appliances, gas cooking and quartz countertops. The spacious master retreat is a personal sanctuary with dual vanities and garden tub. Outside, find your own piece of tranquility featuring a sparkling pool and a sheltered patio, an ideal setup for entertaining guests. Step into this meticulously maintained home and experience the unique blend of comfort, style, and convenience it seamlessly provides.
